# Tai Lieu API FE - ParentController - Registration va PDF - 2026-04-27

Tai lieu nay tong hop 4 API lien quan den registration va enrollment confirmation PDF trong `ParentController.cs`.

Pham vi tai lieu:

- Xem danh sach registration cua be
- Xem chi tiet registration
- Preview du lieu enrollment confirmation PDF
- Xem lich su file enrollment confirmation PDF

## Tong quan role va pham vi du lieu

Tat ca API ben duoi deu nam trong `ParentController` va controller co `[Authorize]`.

| Role | Du lieu duoc xem | Pham vi du lieu | Hanh dong duoc phep |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Parent | Registration va PDF cua cac hoc sinh dang linked voi parent hien tai | `own` | `view` |
| Admin | Khong dung nhom API nay de xem du lieu staff scope | `none` | `none` |
| ManagementStaff | Khong dung nhom API nay | `none` | `none` |
| Teacher | Khong dung nhom API nay | `none` | `none` |
| Student | Khong dung nhom API nay | `none` | `none` |
| Anonymous | Khong duoc truy cap | `none` | `none` |

Ghi chu:

- Code khong dat `[Authorize(Roles = "Parent")]` tren endpoint, nhung handler se verify current user phai co `Parent profile` active.
- Parent chi xem duoc registration cua hoc sinh dang linked voi parent.
- Neu khong truyen `studentProfileId` o API list, backend se uu tien:
  1. `studentId` trong token
  2. hoc sinh dau tien dang linked voi parent

## Dinh dang response chung

Success tu `MatchOk()`:

```json
{
  "isSuccess": true,
  "data": {}
}
```

Error domain/validation:

```json
{
  "type": "https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7231#section-6.5.4",
  "title": "Profile.StudentNotLinkedToParent",
  "status": 404,
  "detail": "Student not linked to this parent"
}
```

Validation pipeline/domain error khac:

```json
{
  "type": "https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7231#section-6.5.1",
  "title": "Registration.InvalidEnrollmentConfirmationPdfFormType",
  "status": 400,
  "detail": "Invalid enrollment confirmation PDF form type: auto2. Allowed values are auto, new, newStudent, continuing, continuingStudent."
}
```

