## Status definition

### RegistrationStatus

| Status | Y nghia |
| --- | --- |
| `New` | Moi tao registration |
| `WaitingForClass` | Dang cho xep lop |
| `ClassAssigned` | Da co lop, chua vao hoc ngay theo logic he thong |
| `Studying` | Dang hoc |
| `Paused` | Dang bao luu |
| `Completed` | Da hoan thanh |
| `Cancelled` | Da huy |

### EntryType

| Value | Y nghia |
| --- | --- |
| `Immediate` | Vao hoc ngay / hoc cac buoi con lai |
| `Wait` | Cho lop moi |
| `Retake` | Thi lai / vao lop sau retake |

### OperationType

| Value | Y nghia |
| --- | --- |
| `Initial` | Dang ky lan dau |
| `Upgrade` | Nang goi hoc |
| `Renewal` | Gia han |
| `Transfer` | Chuyen lop |
| `TransferBranch` | Chuyen chi nhanh |
| `Retake` | Thi lai |

### FormType cua PDF

| Value | Y nghia |
| --- | --- |
| `auto` | Backend tu resolve form type |
| `newStudent` | Mau hoc vien moi |
| `continuingStudent` | Mau hoc vien tiep tuc |

## Luong chuyen trang thai

Luong tong quat cua registration:

1. Staff tao registration -> `New`
2. Cho xep lop -> `WaitingForClass`
3. Da co lop -> `ClassAssigned` hoac `Studying`
4. Bao luu -> `Paused`
5. Ket thuc -> `Completed`
6. Huy -> `Cancelled`

Parent o nhom API nay chi co quyen `view`, khong co API tac dong de doi status.

## Permission matrix theo role

| API | Parent | Admin | ManagementStaff | Teacher | Student | Anonymous |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `GET /api/parent/registrations` | Yes | No | No | No | No | No |
| `GET /api/parent/registrations/{id}` | Yes | No | No | No | No | No |
| `GET /api/parent/registrations/{id}/enrollment-confirmation-pdf` | Yes | No | No | No | No | No |
| `GET /api/parent/registrations/{id}/enrollment-confirmation-pdf/history` | Yes | No | No | No | No | No |

## Validation rule tong hop

| Rule | API ap dung | Ket qua khi sai |
| --- | --- | --- |
| User phai dang nhap | Tat ca | 401 |
| Current user phai co `Parent profile` active | Tat ca | 404 `Profile.ParentNotFound` |
| Hoc sinh duoc chon phai linked voi parent | List API | 404 `Profile.StudentNotLinkedToParent` |
| Registration phai thuoc ve hoc sinh linked voi parent | Detail/PDF APIs | 404 `Registration.NotFound` |
| `status` query chi filter khi parse duoc enum | List API | Parse fail thi bo qua filter |
| `track` query duoc normalize: chi `secondary` giu nguyen, gia tri khac tro ve `primary` | PDF preview/history | Khong tra loi, mac dinh `primary` |
| `formType` chi nhan `auto`, `new`, `newStudent`, `continuing`, `continuingStudent` | PDF preview/history | 400 `Registration.InvalidEnrollmentConfirmationPdfFormType` |
| Track PDF phai co enrollment active | PDF preview | 404 `Registration.EnrollmentNotFound` |
| Builder preview phai resolve du payment setting va du lieu can thiet | PDF preview | 400/404 loi domain tuong ung |

## Luu y FE quan trong

- `GET /api/parent/registrations` va `GET /api/parent/registrations/{id}` dung cung data shape voi registration staff APIs, nhung scope da bi gioi han theo parent-student link.
- `GET /api/parent/registrations/{id}` da tra `firstStudySession` va `actualStudySchedules`.
- `GET /api/parent/registrations/{id}/enrollment-confirmation-pdf` chi la preview/read-only, khong generate file moi.
- `GET /api/parent/registrations/{id}/enrollment-confirmation-pdf/history` tra `pdfUrl` da qua `fileStorage.GetDownloadUrl()` neu tao duoc download URL.